gomodel:SYNGO_2058  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099060 replaced by GO:0099634" , "Rationale: \"Silver-intensified immunogold reaction for the α2 subunit revealed intense labeling of symmetric synapses (Figures 4C,D).\"\n\nNote: staining is more centered around the postsynapse. No quantification was included.\n\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: \"Functional expression of the GABAA receptor α2 and α3 subunits at synapses between intercalated medial paracapsular neurons of mouse amygdala\"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0593-3443" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" ;
        dc:date           "2024-03-14" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_CC_2058" ;
